                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10229" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1532</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">276 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孤岛采油厂“五到区块”油藏经营价值管理体系的构建之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Construction Process of the &quot;Five-to-Block&quot; Reservoir Operation Value Management System in Gudao Oil Production Plant</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">付代红，范雯雯，王兴懿，伊力亚尔•托乎提</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（华东）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油化工股份有限公司胜利油田分公司孤岛采油厂</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石油工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">油藏经营；价值管理；油藏区块；数智转型；五到区块；2025百优案例；过期专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Reservoir Operation; Value Management; Reservoir Block; Digital-intelligence Transformation; Five-to-Block</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为胜利油田陆上产油量第一大厂，孤岛采油厂构建了“五到区块”油藏经营价值管理体系，在对油藏区块进行清晰界定的基础上，以业财数智化转型支持算清油藏效益账。通过“目标分解到区块、决策优化到区块、核算管理到区块、分析评价到区块、考核激励到区块”，实现了油藏经营价值规划、决策、计量、分析、分配的全过程闭环管理，助力油藏高效益开发和企业高质量发展。本案例聚焦一场主题报告会，站在总会计师高洪科的视角，梳理了孤岛采油厂以“五到区块”目标管理试点实践为契机，解决核心问题、拓展方法路径，从单点突破到系统串联、从实践探索到理论升华，逐步构建油藏经营价值管理体系的过程。引导学员理解油藏经营价值管理的本质，结合油藏经营的特征剖析其价值管理的重点及难点，深入思考业财数智化转型在油藏经营价值管理体系中的作用，进而拓展探讨油藏经营价值管理体系的持续优化问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As the largest oil production plant on land in Shengli Oilfield, Gudao Oil Production Plant has established a &quot;Five-to-Block&quot; reservoir operation value management system. Based on a clear definition of reservoir blocks, it supports the calculation of reservoir benefits through the digital transformation of business and finance. By &quot;decomposing goals to blocks, optimizing decisions to blocks, managing accounting to blocks, analyzing and evaluating to blocks, and incentivizing to blocks&quot;, it has achieved a closed-loop management of the entire process of reservoir operation value planning, decision-making, measurement, analysis, and distribution, promoting the high-efficiency development of reservoirs and the high-quality development of the enterprise. This case focuses on a theme report meeting, from the perspective of Chief Accountant Gao Hongke, it sorts out the process of Gudao Oil Production Plant gradually building a reservoir operation value management system by taking the &quot;Five-to-Block&quot; target management pilot practice as an opportunity to solve core problems, expand methods and paths, from single-point breakthrough to system connection, from practical exploration to theoretical elevation. It guides students to understand the essence of reservoir operation value management, analyzes the key points and difficulties of value management based on the characteristics of reservoir operation, deeply considers the role of business and finance digital transformation in the reservoir operation value management system, and then expands the discussion on the continuous optimization of the reservoir operation value management system.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《财务管理》、《管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">油藏经营管理；价值管理；数智化转型理论；投入产出理论；协同管理理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
